                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17960622-40-off219 t17960622-40-cd220"></join>, a pair of silver shoe buckles, value 21s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17960622-40-victim460" type="victimName">
                     William 
                     Edwards
